file.name: api.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Create Now API
  description: 作成したapi

servers:
  - url: http://192.168.50.10:3000/v1

paths:
  /pdf:
    post:
      description: PDFを作成
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
                - content
              properties:
                content:
                  type: array
                  items:
                    type: object
      responses:
        "200":
          description: 成功した場合、PDFファイルを返す
          content:
            application/pdf:
              schema:
                type: string
                format: binary
        "400":
          $ref: "#/components/responses/400Error"

components:
  responses:
    400Error:
      description: Invalid request
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            type: object
            properties:
              message:
                type: string
